OpenFlow.NBAPI
Class FlowModSpec

java.lang.Object
  OpenFlow.NBAPI.SBMatchFilterSpec
      OpenFlow.NBAPI.FlowModSpec

public class FlowModSpec
extends SBMatchFilterSpec

Aids in creation of flow modification messages.

Extends the SBMatchFilterSpec class to include the additional fields used for creating an OpenFlow flow modification message. Minimal range checking is performed on values (i.e., that they are within range of the target SB message field element size) for all set<Field>() methods that return a boolean. Otherwise, no range checking is performed on the field values.

The SBMatchFilterSpec parameters are used to set the MessagePB.SBOFMessagePB.OFMessagePB.OFFlowModPB.match field.
